{"tid":1826312,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"做左激光矯視 差d同男朋友分手 ...","createTime":"2020-01-16T04:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T04:16:08.000Z","uid":1734,"like":6,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6d6b0f83737b663e9f9870b6cea236459475676b","tid":1826312,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:43:25.000Z","msg":"我男朋友一直都係不折不扣既眼鏡控，一齊個時就已經成日話我戴眼鏡好靚，不過我覺得自己戴唔戴眼鏡都好睇，人靚呢d小事影響唔到啦<br />\n<br />\n但自己都多做運動，有時戴眼鏡做真係冇咁方便，又想俾個驚喜男朋友，就襯佢同朋友去旅行個陣做左激光矯視<br />\n<br />\n點知佢番到黎見我冇戴眼鏡已經黑面問我做咩突然戴con，知道我偷偷地做激光矯視就就發晒脾氣，話唔鍾意咁樣，話我好唔尊重佢，想同我分手<br />\n<br />\n我同佢都一齊左6年，冇理由咁樣就分？我以為佢係隨便搵個藉口同我分開，但同佢好認真傾完之後，佢同我講自己接受唔到冇戴眼鏡既男仔<br />\n<br />\n於是我依家同佢出街都要戴番副眼鏡做裝飾....."},{"pid":"4955f4ecd69d3aa1c34394d49f43a7f0134b8338","tid":1826312,"uid":199902,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:45:22.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"ee4923cb37323706626d472d02e9f5fb3a1ba994","tid":1826312,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:52:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e1054e7bee422ac85124c6e153ce4b6cddf0d2","tid":1826312,"uid":249976,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:54:03.000Z","msg":"gay<br />\n零分重作"},{"pid":"26fdc9540ffb5e7a21b3ce17965778f5f7204635","tid":1826312,"uid":34929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:56:04.000Z","msg":"This is gay"},{"pid":"82c95f70ff853f804566f9de31f58d7dc1b49234","tid":1826312,"uid":296607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:56:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kmN8np72x-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkmN8np72x-0&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GDbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=17660def\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kmN8np72x-0</a><br />\n 777宣戰<br />\n<br />\n柒婆︰「唔好因為一時嘅誤會欠缺左對於一國兩制；對於基本法嘅理解，而去破壞呢個咁重要嘅原則同方針，否則佢地自己<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>&mdash;&mdash;今日擔心出現嘅情況可能係佢地自己一手造成</strong></span></span>」</div><br />\n<br />\n睇下佢幾撚囂張<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLvjzsJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLvjzsJ.jpg&h=2419d35b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4da7bd370107ae060a3feedc66e9557741dcb29b","tid":1826312,"uid":71423,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"小妹都試過 最後都係做多次矯視整返近視追返男朋友"},{"pid":"6a679a31bcd4d0382f37f8fafa37961812ab3a29","tid":1826312,"uid":258598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:31:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"113dc5d0a6917a770c3bd10b0ef7af9801073138","tid":1826312,"uid":86745,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:35:17.000Z","msg":"仲以為矯完視先望到男友好樣衰要分手"},{"pid":"4559e04e7378a9f596adcbedebcea0807512b12f","tid":1826312,"uid":6446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:38:02.000Z","msg":"冇度數眼鏡囉 <br />\n假膠 拉"},{"pid":"7a8c83dc1f152f6a642a48151aadb039d9d4c5c3","tid":1826312,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4559e04e7378a9f596adcbedebcea0807512b12f","tid":1826312,"uid":6446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:38:02.000Z","msg":"冇度數眼鏡囉 <br />\n假膠 拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:41:02.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"e23a61ab40ed10f14e2fd9a16ef5d4a20fd7e1bc","tid":1826312,"uid":67771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82c95f70ff853f804566f9de31f58d7dc1b49234","tid":1826312,"uid":296607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:56:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kmN8np72x-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkmN8np72x-0&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GDbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=17660def\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kmN8np72x-0</a><br />\n 777宣戰<br />\n<br />\n柒婆︰「唔好因為一時嘅誤會欠缺左對於一國兩制；對於基本法嘅理解，而去